# Online Banking Software

## 11.1 Users & Security

### 11.1.1 User Account Management
- Add, view, edit, and delete user accounts.

### 11.1.2 Authentication & Sessions
- Manage user authentication (Password + MFA).
- Automatic logout after inactivity.
- Manage active sessions and connected devices.

### 11.1.3 Activity Logs
- View account activity logs (logins, updates, transfers, etc.).

---

## 11.2 Account Management

### 11.2.1 Account Operations
- Add, view, and close bank accounts (Savings and Checking accounts).

### 11.2.2 Account Overview
- Display balances, masked account numbers, and recent transactions.

### 11.2.3 Statements
- Download monthly account statements (PDF or CSV format).

---

## 11.3 Transaction Management

### 11.3.1 Transaction History
- View transaction history and details.
- Filter or search by date, amount, or merchant.
- Distinguish between pending and cleared transactions.

### 11.3.2 Categorization
- Manage transaction categories (auto or manual).
- Support for custom tags.

### 11.3.3 Transfers
- Perform money transfers:
  - Internal (between userâ€™s own accounts).
  - External (to linked external bank accounts).

### 11.3.4 Notes & Receipts
- Add optional notes or attach digital receipts to transactions.
